# Rules and Standards

## Code Style Guide
- Favour Python and Bash for scripts
- Use clear, descriptive names
- Consistent indentation and formatting

## Naming Rules
- Use kebab-case for files, snake_case for variables
- Persona and prompt files must match their names

## Lint Config References
- Use flake8 for Python
- Use shellcheck for Bash

